                                text="&lt;p>&lt;span class=&quot;light-font&quot;>&lt;span class=&quot;body-unica-32-reg&quot;>Millions are blind because of glaucoma but connecting with patients sooner could help them get to a doctor before they lose their vision.&lt;/span>&lt;/span>&lt;/p>&#xd;&#xa;"
